UID:564@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260611
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260612
SUMMARY:BWA Y3: Year 3 Indian Bollywood Dance Performance
DESCRIPTION:Year 3 pupils will perform their Indian Bollywood dance. Dress up is encouraged (traditional Indian costume or vibrant colours).\n\nYear 3 pupils have been learning an 'Indian Bollywood’ dance. Parents are invited to watch the final performance. Pupils should come dressed up in their costume on the day and bring their uniform in a bag. A member of staff will meet parents at the gate at 9.00 to escort you into the school.
CATEGORIES:ARTS
