UID:550@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260619
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260620
SUMMARY:BWA Y3: Sports Day -  Year 2 & 3
DESCRIPTION:Sports Day for Year 3 and 3B. Volunteers needed to walk with classes to the common.\n\nParents and carers are requested to meet at the school at 12:30pm to help supervise the journey to the common. Please confirm availability by email by the end of the school day today.
CATEGORIES:SPORTS
END:VEVENT
