UID:592@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260901
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260902
SUMMARY:BWA: Wandsworth Music -  Instrumental Lessons Sign-up
DESCRIPTION:Information regarding instrumental and vocal music lessons for the upcoming Autumn 2026 term.\n\nWandsworth Music is offering small group and individual lessons for the next school year. Parents can sign up via the Wandsworth Music website. The Music Academy also offers various ensembles on Saturdays, Wednesdays, and Tuesdays at Burntwood School and West Hill Primary School.
CATEGORIES:ARTS
END:VEVENT
