UID:594@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260608
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260609
SUMMARY:BWA Y3: Year 3 RSE Lessons
DESCRIPTION:Information regarding the upcoming PSHCE and RSE lessons focusing on 'Changes'.\n\nNext half term, Year 3 will be exploring the theme 'Changes' in PSCHE lessons, covering relationships, friendships, and online safety. Please contact the class teacher via the school admin email for questions.
