SUMMARY:BWA Y3: Year 3 Trip to Lavender Hill Pizza Express
DESCRIPTION:Year 3 will visit Lavender Hill Pizza Express for a STEM and DT food flavours session.\n\nYear 3 will be taking a trip to Lavender Hill Pizza Express to learn about food flavours and food safety. Children will create their own pizzas. The trip departs school at 9am and returns at 12pm. Consent is required via School Gateway by Friday 19th June. Two parent volunteers are requested to join from 8:50am.
CATEGORIES:TRIP
END:VEVENT
