DESCRIPTION:Deadline for parent consent and volunteer requests for the Year 3 Pizza Express trip.\n\nDeadline to provide consent for the Year 3 trip to Lavender Hill Pizza Express via School Gateway. Parent volunteers must also submit their requests by this date.
