UID:578@bwa-calendar
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260703
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260705
SUMMARY:BWA: Hair Day
DESCRIPTION:Crazy Hair Day for all students across all streams.\n\nWe encourage all children (All Streams All Schools) to come to school with their craziest hairstyles. It's going to be a fun-filled day! Children can come to school with their craziest hair styles! Whether it’s rainbow mohawks, glittery spikes, animal-shaped hair, or colorful braids, we want to see it all! We encourage you to get involved and help your child create their wild hairstyle. Let’s make this a memorable day for everyone!
CATEGORIES:COMMUNITY
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR